Package: ImmuPop
Type: Package
Title: Estimating Population Immunity Using Individual Antibody Titers
Version: 0.1.1
Authors@R:
    c(person(given = "Tim",
             family = "Tsang",
             role = c("aut", "cre"),
             email = "timkltsang@gmail.com"),
      person(given = "Weijia",
             family = "Xiong",
             role = "aut",
             email = "wjxiong@connect.hku.hk"))
Description: Estimate population immunity metrics from individual serology
    data, including geometric mean titer (GMT), proportion of non-naive
    individuals, population immune proportion, and relative reduction in
    reproductive number (R0). Uses bootstrap sampling and MCMC-based
    Dirichlet estimation with age-structured contact matrices.
